
Generate a buildable source tree (after git checkout)
--------------------------------
autoreconf -iv


Hack away
---------
Update changelog, source, api doc, builds autoscan nd tests
run tests: cd test && ./setupRun.sh
merge (or request pull) into current development branch


Merge development branch
------------------------
Get the api doc diffs and update the website
git merge the development branch into master
bump the configure.ac version number
consolidate Changelog


Create a source tarball (suitable for distribution)
-----------------------
autoreconf -iv
autoscan
make distcheck


